Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机是9点55分由羽田起飞\NJNA903航次 飞往那霸的班机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中小姐 要不要来联谊啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是之前\N我说的海军陆战队M6
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔 真的飞起来了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要 你也过来看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从昨天开始就怪怪的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟相良有关吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎么突然说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好\N这个话题到此结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 歪了一边耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 只是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气明明这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#04 KID NAP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想死看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然就没有人会驾驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我早就想开开看这种飞机了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉似乎比开运输机愉快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际开起来的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要杀我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你愉不愉快啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 来看戏的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要杀掉驾驶员？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙骗我说飞机故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么要返回羽田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要享受杀人是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们机会的是我的祖国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做会增加作战危险性的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么讲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要对方肯听话 我也很绅士的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你也听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照同伴的策略\N我尽量不杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要是反抗的话 我就杀别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往北飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终的目的地是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在十分稀有的完全独裁国家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良 你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是联合国的F16耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会飞到这种地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不要告诉别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲绳周边应该都是海吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 从刚才到现在都是山耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问一下空中小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说 她好像都没过来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是冲绳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说是冲绳了\N这里根本就不是日本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…到达宴会会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是冲绳吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良 那个是米格21耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那台战车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是T-54式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年前的破铜烂铁耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然又是最先进的RK92
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然都是苏联制的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过差距好像太大了点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机内的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我代替机长成为本机的负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机由于不得已的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落在兴凯自治区的空军基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么都不知道？\N克制一点 学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点发现好不好 老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位将在这个拥有复杂政治情势\N以及充满惊险刺激之处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为我们的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像很欢迎各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若打算逃亡\N或是做出可疑举动时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会毫不留情的射杀各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了要防止这种事态\N才毁灭敌人基地的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子 除了KGB以外\N似乎还有其他幕后黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴凯自治区…似乎也不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都只是\N被操纵的棋子罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被某个不知名人物所煽动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不知名的人物\N就只为了绑架一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅抓了400人以上的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还选择了很难靠政治手段\N救出人质的场所是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将劫机这种老套的恐怖手法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运用得如此巧妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得人质能够\N平安被释放的机率有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不包括千鸟…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 只要我们不轻举妄动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟要以外的400人\N或许会很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴凯自治区政府也不希望\N情势再更加紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死数百个日本人\N对他们一点好处也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应先以外交管道交涉\N等人质被释放后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再寻找千鸟的下落并将其救出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论上很正确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先观望一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 反正还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且敌人体内也存在着剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待他的连络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长发的漂亮姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要拍个寄给新闻媒体的影片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能出来拍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你挺上相的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我怎么行呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看也知道\N我只不过是个穷酸丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会让观众感到不愉快而已\N真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你来就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等一下 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 我不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你想对我的学生做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 马上就会还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓的话就抓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓你就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是要给媒体的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种藉口对我是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有你们这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然做出劫机这种最低级的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还利用小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的主张根本就等于垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么理由\N做这种事神绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你实在有够吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会痛啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群人已经没有利用价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 我自己会走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫医生来！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了蠢事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要考量到\N当它在地面启动时的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多的话保证没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面不是有条红色的电线吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿掉绝缘胶带\N插进写着“3”的插座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 我要插了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再去动任何地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30公尺之内\N行动电话跟无线电都禁止使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果什么时候能知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快明天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太久了 没办法快一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算使用药物\N也要在六小时后才会产生效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话连你一起杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要催我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们根本不知道\NWhispered的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连Chodar都带来了\N亏你们还敢说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止这国家的人变心\N以防万一的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你还蛮胆小的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要闭上嘴巴\N乖乖的把工作做好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相良士官 B-3128 Uruz7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良 你没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校大人 我的回答是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良士官 说明现在状况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然做出这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推断他们打算杀光乘客\N以隐瞒绑架千鸟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要瓦解他们非常困难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我自己现在的装备\N完全无法对付他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我们会拟定策略
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现阶段乘客的安全\N要比救出千鸟重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫机犯的首领是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他至今已暗杀了\N30名以上的重要人士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还曾经二度引爆航空客机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个危险的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我们被KGB追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龙便是KGB所雇用的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙趁我们不在时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率领两架AS\N袭击了游击队的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村庄几乎全毁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发誓要报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了两周后 我们有了机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我当诱饵 相良士官负责狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了九龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是残忍的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他根本就不是\N会释放人质的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:16:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来必须让那个叫九龙的人\N付出很大的代价才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过来这边 慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 你在跟哪里连络？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我通讯的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为靠空手能赢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不过还要再继续喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我回去好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再做这种\N奇怪的睡眠学习…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在出生前就知道这些事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都要迅速进行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们叫计程车飙很快了说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们Tuatha De Danaan\N即将实行的作战计划如下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在AS小队6机出发前\N先由各个航空支援部队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照攻击直升机、运输直升机\N垂直起降战斗机的顺序出动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的问题是大型炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测此炸弹应为遥控式引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要比第一波攻击后\N展开还击的恐怖份子更快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们按下引爆钮前\N先拆除这个炸弹不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两架运输机\N在作战开始同时强行降落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在5分钟内收容\N巨无霸客机内的人质后起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有5分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太难了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分就够久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保护那庞然大物的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在降落时\N若其中一架运输机遭到破坏呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剩下的人质\N尽可能的收容至运输直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后舍弃装载AS也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但届时一定要将AS彻底破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点比各位的生命都重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够成功达成这项作战的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界只有我们而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待各位的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良那边有连络吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟敌人不是普通角色…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一件事我能肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我所知 那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未因为个人感情因素\N而导致判断错误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的枪声是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 从里面传来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在会冲出去的家伙\N绝对是超级愚蠢的外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不一样
